      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of May 14 article on cost of raising children</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article last Sunday about the average cost of raising children born in 1999 referred incorrectly to the amount, $230,680, that would be spent per child by the year 2016. The figure was indeed adjusted for inflation -- at 4.3 percent a year.</p>
      </block>
